name: SPACEPRIME
description:
You deliver packages for SPACEPRIME, the leading retailer in the year 2XXX. However, the company is halfway through a system update, so your spaceship's console is giving you instructions that conflict with the manual. Your job is to figure out how to fix your ship before it breaks down completely!

INSTRUCTIONS: Game requires a manual to be properly played. It can be found here:

http://imgur.com/a/uhueB

Game made for the first ArtUp Interactive Jam in a team of three.
